text: Sébastien Bonmalais (born 6 February 1998 in Saint-Pierre, Reunion Island) is a French professional squash player. As of August 2018, he was ranked number 100 in the world. He won the 2017 Gibraltar Open and the 2017 Guatemala Open. ==References== Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:French male squash players
